This paper discusses the development of a neural network model that can represent and store logical relations, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the redesigning of neurons and links, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the construction of rule libraries for expert systems, which is a topic related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CL, and cs.CC, in that order.
